{"tid":1490608,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"翻譯咗 #1490291 ［整理］黑警醫院凌虐長者經過","createTime":"2019-08-20T07:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T07:42:20.000Z","uid":101022,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dd0e18005a5ee9bb93e4d38269cc70f4594424f4","tid":1490608,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:08:59.000Z","msg":"［整理］黑警醫院凌虐長者經過<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1490291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1490291</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請文宣執執<br />\n<br />\n2019年6月25日晚上約11時，<br />\n62歲男事主醉酒與人爭執被捕，<br />\n後被送到北區醫院。<br />\n<br />\nOn the night June 25, 2019, the victim was drunk and in conflict with someone. He was arrested and sent to North District Hospital.<br />\n<br />\n事主四肢因醉酒被綁於病床，<br />\n整個人無法郁動，然後被送到紊亂獨立病房。該病房為單人病房，只能容納一張病床。<br />\n<br />\nVictim was bound on patient bed tightly as long as he was drunk and uncontrollable. He was then passed to an independent room. The room is for single person, which only provide space for one bed only.<br />\n<br />\n病房內設有閉路電視系統（醫管局：病房若加裝明顯鏡頭 會被某些病人拆下）<br />\n所以病房設有的是 隱密的鏡頭。<br />\n病房外亦有通告說明病房內有鏡頭及會進行錄影。<br />\n<br />\nEach independent room has its hidden CCTV. According to Hospital Authority, obvious camera could be removed by the patient in some cases. There is reminders to users outside the room.<br />\n<br />\n當日凌晨時間，<br />\n事主多次被至少兩個軍裝警員凌虐，<br />\n<br />\nAt that night, the victim has been abused by two armoured police.<br />\n<br />\n1. 包括用警棍插下體 再放近頭部<br />\nInclude using baton hitting victim&rsquo;s sex organ, and put the baton again back near his head.<br />\n2. 拳打下體及腹部<br />\nPunches on sex organ and abdomen.<br />\n3. 將手腕拗向床邊欄杆<br />\nBending victim&rsquo;s palm towards the bed railing.<br />\n4. 用毛巾 上衣掩蓋口鼻<br />\nCovered up victim&rsquo;s nosed and mouth with towel and his clothes.<br />\n5. 撐大眼睛用強光照射<br />\nForces victim&rsquo;s eye opened and shine it directly by torch <br />\n6. 在耳邊大叫<br />\nShouted next to victim&rsquo;s ear<br />\n7. 掌摑<br />\nSlap on his face<br />\n8. 扯腳毛<br />\nPick hair from victim&rsquo;s legs<br />\n9. 大力擠壓眼睛位置<br />\nSqueezed area around victim&rsquo;s eye<br />\n10. 恐嚇事主會對其家人不利<br />\n在其耳邊 逐個讀出家人名字和住址 <br />\n稱：我會搞你老婆同兩個仔<br />\nScared victim by hurting him and his family after reading the full names and living addresses of his family members."},{"pid":"5ea2a9c9c5ca367443a32e69240533b01a1dddbc","tid":1490608,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:09:14.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"409aa2864d5f0608abfc2ea6e770aed45700692d","tid":1490608,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:09:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bb452c490327f8d492cf7cc5179e69313882466","tid":1490608,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:09:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e96e3c07e6f9573346cfefb633981d227cee012c","tid":1490608,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:10:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c7a553acc0fc2b240b2820fc35a1e2fca58dabc","tid":1490608,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:10:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e7df15c637e4f0cf51a3c6383ffbbae142da0a","tid":1490608,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:10:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8487cd5f3d64796eb49d473df21bba641fae4f1b","tid":1490608,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:11:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89be096e02963942659935db25ac7d11a4e0c5eb","tid":1490608,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:13:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f47aef632a98e99623629d7ca06a7e76dbf0d8c2","tid":1490608,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e47cf356bee8841f93592af8ff55194